data.description: Fantastic 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the Deer Creek School District. This Castleberry addition offers a neighborhood pool, fitness facility, clubhouse, & playground. Open concept living & dining area leads to the kitchen which features custom wood cabinets, quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances, & a breakfast bar for additional seating! Covered back patio & fully fenced back yard!
